{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_FireDChase}}
'''A_FireDChase'''<br />
(no parameters)

Similar to [[A_FastChase]], it makes the calling actor strafe while closing in on their target, but without changing its base speed. It also makes the calling actor bob up and down while remaining at least 64 map units above the floor. It uses the <tt>special1</tt> and <tt>special2</tt> fields to keep track of the bobbing and strafing motions.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|FireDemon}} and derived classes.

